<lyrics>[V1]
 1- myn gẖyrk btrạb ạlạ̉rḍ yqdr ykẖlq ʿyn lḍryr
 wyrjʿ lnhạrh ạlḍy bʿd mạ ʿạsẖ llḍlmẗ ạ̉syr
 ạlqrạr- ạ̹nt ʿẓym wqdyr ḥbk ḥb kbyr
 nyrk hyn mạ ạ̹nt ḥnyn msẖ mmkn ttgẖyr ywm
 mạbtʿjzsẖ ạ̹ydyk wlạ sẖyʾ ṣʿb ʿlyk
 tsẖfy bklmẗ wtḥyy ạlmyt wtfrḥ qlby ạlmhmwm
 2- qlbk klh mḥbẗ yạ rb wạ̹nt ạlfrḥẗ fy kl zmạn
 ạ̹nt ạlrạʿy wạ̹nt ạlạ̉b wạ̉ml kl tʿysẖ yỷsạn
 3- lw ywm hạn ạlḍny̱ ʿ ạlạ̉m lw nsyth ạ̹nt mạtnsạsẖ
 ḥḍnk ạ̹nt kbyr byḍm qlbk ṭyb wmạbtqsạsẖ</lyrics>
<title>myn gẖyrk btrạb ạlạ̉rḍ</title>
</song>